```plantuml
@startuml IBM_IBM-Spectrum-Scale-Security-Posture

actor "Cron Scheduler" as cron
participant "cronjob.py" as cronjob
participant "fetch_security_posture_and_upload_to_ES.sh" as fetcher
participant "Spectrum Scale Cluster" as cluster
participant "security_posture.py" as collector
participant "split_json_for_kibana.py" as splitter
participant "Elasticsearch" as es
participant "Kibana" as kibana

cron -> cronjob: Trigger scheduled execution
cronjob -> fetcher: Execute main script
fetcher -> cluster: SSH connection
cluster -> collector: Execute security_posture.py
collector --> cluster: Collect security data
cluster --> fetcher: Return raw JSON data
fetcher -> splitter: Process JSON data
splitter --> fetcher: Split JSON files
fetcher -> es: Delete old indices (DELETE)
fetcher -> es: Upload cluster data (POST)
fetcher -> es: Upload filesystem data (POST)
fetcher -> es: Upload exports data (POST)
es --> kibana: Index data for visualization
fetcher --> cronjob: Return status
cronjob --> cron: Completion status

@enduml
```